title: Dev makes all Black Ops 3 campaign levels playable from the get-go
text:
Dev makes all Black Ops 3 campaign levels playable from the get-go 
Published By: Gamasutra.com - Today 
This year's Call Of Duty game will have a single-player campaign that can be played however you like, as devs say traditional level progress...
